headline.main: Stone Wins Sunshine Tour Order of Merit
headline.print_headline: Stone Wins Sunshine Tour Order of Merit

lead_paragraph: Brandon Stone was declared winner of southern Africa’s Sunshine Tour order of merit on Saturday even though he is in Mexico for the WGC-Mexico Championship.
